title: #275: Fed Up Strays
description:
Timestamps below! The Real Housewives of Atlanta finished the season with a green Kenya and a Fed raid. Over on RHOP, the arguments over manners continue. Spoiler alert: no one has them. Top Chef named the top two finalists, and we also got to look at David Copperfield’s oddness. PLUS: Camille Grammar tweets and Ben gets trolled.

Timestamps
0-36:45 Chatter and Crappens Mailbag: Real Househusbands, Real OBGYNs of Everywhere
36:45-1:22:20 RHOA season finale
1:22:20-1:35:25 Top Chef Finale Part 1
1:35:25 Clear the Flem: #Ryebread
1:39:40 RHOPotomac Ruined Trip
